Automaticall increase / decrease the desired of number of ECS Tasksk
AMAZON EC2 auto scaling uses AWS application Auto Scaling
  EC2 Service average CPU utilization
  EC2 Service average memory utilization
  ALB Requests count per target - metric coming from the ALB
Target trecking --- scale based on target value for a specific cloudwatch metric
Step scaling -- scale based on a specific CloudWatch alarm
Scheduled scaling -- scale based on a specified date/time
ECS Service auto scaling is not EC2 auto scaling!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Fargate auto scaling is much easier on setup (serverless)

--------------------

EC2 Launch type - ASG EC2

Accomodate ECS service scaling by adding underlying EC2 instances
Auto scaling group scaling
  scale your ASG based on CPU utilization
  Add ec2 instances over time
ECS cluster capacity provider 
  used to automatically provision and scale the infrastructure for your ECS Tasks
  capacity provider paired with ASG
  Add EC2 instances when your missing capacity

